ind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/\"},{\"title\":\"DeepMind claims its newest AI tool is a whiz at math and science problems | TechCrunch\",\"url\":\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/05/14/deepmind-claims-its-newest-ai-tool-is-a-whiz-at-math-and-science-problems/\"},{\"title\":\"Can AI evolve itself? DeepMind's AlphaEvolve shows it's possible\",\"url\":\"https://www.newsbytesapp.com/news/science/deepmind-s-new-ai-tool-excels-at-solving-math-science-problems/story\"},{\"title\":\"DeepMind's AlphaEvolve Surpasses Expectations in Solving Math and Science Problems | AI News\",\"url\":\"https://opentools.ai/news/deepminds-alphaevolve-surpasses-expectations-in-solving-math-and-science-problems\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about AlphaEvolve, DeepMind's automated evaluation system:\n\n## Overview\n\nAlphaEvolve is an AI system designed by DeepMind to tackle complex problems in math and science with \"machine-gradable\" solutions.\n\n## Automated Evaluation Metrics & Machine-Gradable Verifier\n\nThe core of AlphaEvolve's approach centers on automated evaluation:\n\n- Every iteration proposed by the pair of LLMs is accepted or rejected based on a user-supplied \"evaluate\" function that returns machine-gradable metrics.\n\n- This mechanism takes the form of a function mapping a solution to a set of scalar evaluation metrics.\n\n- AlphaEvolve verifies, runs and scores the proposed programs using automated evaluation metrics that provide an objective, quantifiable assessment of each solution's accuracy and quality.\n\n## How It Works\n\nAlphaEvolve utilizes an ensemble of Google's Gemini models: the faster Gemini Flash explores a wide array of potential ideas, while the more powerful Gemini Pro provides deep, insightful suggestions for computer programs that implement these algorithmic solutions. These generated programs then undergo automated evaluation using metrics that objectively assess each solution's accuracy and quality.\n\nThe orchestrator is described as an \"evolutionary algorithm that gradually develops programs that improve the score on the automated evaluation metrics.\"\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"95a2efaa-19c7-4ded-ba4a-2403fd275fb4","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:34:48.421Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"AlphaEvolve DeepMind automated evaluation metrics machine-gradable verifier evaluation function","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01JmeaZ3FBREGH3GSEAwtQUM","content":[{"title":"Google DeepMind's AlphaEvolve: A Breakthrough in AI-Driven Scientific Discovery","url":"https://theoutpost.ai/news-story/google-deep-mind-s-alpha-evolve-a-breakthrough-in-ai-driven-algorithm-discovery-15378/"},{"title":"Google DeepMind Unveils AlphaEvolve AI Agent to Tackle Code and Math Challenges","url":"https://winbuzzer.com/2025/05/14/google-deepmind-unveils-alphaevolve-ai-agent-to-tackle-code-and-math-challenges-xcxwbn/"},{"title":"Google DeepMind Unveils AlphaEvolve AI Agent to Tackle Code and Math Challenges - NewsBreak","url":"https://www.newsbreak.com/winbuzzer-com-302470011/4007627574963-google-deepmind-unveils-alphaevolve-ai-agent-to-tackle-code-and-math-challenges"},{"title":"Google’s AlphaEvolve: The AI agent that reclaimed 0.7% of Google’s compute – and how to copy it","url":"https://dnyuz.com/2025/05/16/googles-alphaevolve-the-ai-agent-that-reclaimed-0-7-of-googles-compute-and-how-to-copy-it/"},{"title":"Google’s AlphaEvolve: The AI agent that reclaimed 0.7% of Google’s compute – and how to copy it | VentureBeat","url":"https://venturebeat.com/ai/googles-alphaevolve-the-ai-agent-that-reclaimed-0-7-of-googles-compute-and-how-to-copy-it"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A coding agent for scientific and algorithmic discovery","url":"https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/DeepMind.com/Blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-adv